
Option 1
  - file permissions
    - user readable = can only be seen by webserver - imports, configs, passwords, etc..
    - group readable = project admins - admin files
    - global readable = can be loaded by anyone - normal jxp, js, images, etc...
  - /init.js 660 - this is loaded first
  - then people can do whatever they want
  

Option 2
  /
  /init.js - 
  /www/
  /include/
  /import/
  /logs/

Option 3
  /
  /CONF
  /CONF/init.js
  /CONF/lib/
  ...

Option 4
  /
  /_init.js
  

